###Naming Conventions

Tables: snake_case, plural (e.g., users, exam_submissions)
Columns: snake_case (e.g., created_at, user_id)
Foreign keys: <table>_id (e.g., exam_id, teacher_id)
Indexes: idx_<table>_<columns> (e.g., idx_exams_teacher_id)